text: Justine Caldwell is an American politician and is a Democratic member of the Rhode Island House of Representatives, representing District 30 (East Greenwich, Rhode Island and West Greenwich, Rhode Island). ==Education== Caldwell attended and earned a bachelor's and master's degrees from the University of Rhode Island.
